{
  "name": "Forkfall",
  "title": "Chapter IV — Forkfall",
  "objective": "Cross the drowned saltworks to the twin city — raise the three causeway pylons to settle the fork.",
  "time": 700,
  "story": true,
  "chapter": 4,
  "expedition": true,
  "theme": "saltworks",
  "intro": [
    {
      "title": "Forkfall",
      "lines": [
        "The timeline forked here, out where the tide eats the old works.",
        "A whole city, copied street for street across the brine scar.",
        "Three pylons, strung along the causeways. One city gets to be real."
      ],
      "art": "forkfall"
    }
  ],
  "modifiers": {
    "waves": [
      {
        "at": 300,
        "letters": "ssrr",
        "edge": "w"
      },
      {
        "at": 480,
        "letters": "rrsv",
        "edge": "e"
      }
    ]
  },
  "outro": [
    {
      "title": "One City",
      "lines": [
        "The false branch thins to brine-haze and is gone. One city. One history.",
        "On the far jetty, Mirra Vex waves goodbye across the settled water. Once."
      ],
      "art": "forkfall"
    }
  ],
  "captiveChars": [
    "boomer",
    "helix"
  ],
  "npcs": [
    {
      "id": "mirra-vex-west",
      "name": "Mirra Vex",
      "lines": [
        "You walked in from the west bank. Good. That means you're the real one.",
        "There is a me across the seam. There was never a me across the seam.",
        "The tide funnels everything onto the bridges — get a barricade up at each causeway mouth before the next push.",
        "Three pylons, one quorum. The Anchor settles, and one of these cities stops having happened.",
        "Mind the Brine Hulks — they go straight for your walls. Repair, or watch a flank flood."
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "mirra-vex-east",
      "name": "Mirra Vex",
      "lines": [
        "You walked in from the east jetty. Good. That means you're the real one.",
        "There is a me across the seam. There was never a me across the seam.",
        "Take these. Shards, pulled out of the scar. They spend real.",
        "Bog Spitters squat in the channels and salt the crossings with toxin — wait for a clear bridge, then move.",
        "If she told you to trust me — she would never say that."
      ],
      "gift": {
        "shards": 6
      }
    }
  ],
